Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is a place I have to return to with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:20.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}boku tachi wa eien ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will be forever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:23.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}tooi mukashi sou kimeteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}decided long ago in the past{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take back Sanji who was being pressed \Ninto a marriage and left his friends behind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others infiltrated the Whole Cake Island\Nwhere Emperor Big Mom is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chopper and Carrot in the Mirro-world \Ngot back together with
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro, Nami and Jimbei who \Nhad their own troubles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy was on a rampage in the Whole \NCake Chateau looking for Sanji{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:03:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and came across Sanji's sister Reiju.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's not being fooled, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from that, I've done everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why are you going that way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the rendezvous point!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to be there waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Deciding to Say Goodbye!\NSanji and his Straw-Hat Bento!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Straw Hat Luffy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take care of you right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which direction was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that way!\NOkay, let's get out of this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Chobro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay because I'm Chobro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!\NWe're inside the mirror?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei! Why are you with these rats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brulee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is obviously treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you just sought to leave our crew\Nbut got scared by the roulette.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owed Mama for protecting the Fish-Man Island\Nafter Whitebeard died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was leaving,\NI wanted to fulfill my duty to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I only smell death and evil intent\Nfrom that roulette.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roulette?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing that you didn't do it,\N"First Son of the Sea" Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago, my partner spun the roulette\Nasking mercy of Big Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lost his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing is made to kill whoever spins it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's rigged?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is, you idiots!\NMama won't let anyone leave alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's a minor intruder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or an affiliated pirate\Nwho was once loyal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll welcome those who come to her\Nand kill those who leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going!\NWe gotta get Brook, Luffy and Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going!\NYou're over the weight limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Prometheus?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cut Soul King gave me \Nwas deeper than I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's opening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we gotta give this one credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because no one's ever hurt you guys before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama, are you gonna keep \Nthat skeleton here forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:08:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? "That skeleton"?\NPudding-san, how could you call me that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah, of course!\N--{\i1}Too close!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other creature like this!\NIt's a work of soul art!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna carry it around for a while\Nrather than put it in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a fine job with Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect them to pass through\Nthe Seducing Woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've successfully confined them\Nin a book at the Prison Library.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I went to see them too.\NThat serves them right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"That serves them right"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you gonna kill them?\N--Yeah, after the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent bargirls to everyone in Germa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're drunk by now\Nand totally unsuspecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. But Reiju was snooping around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:09:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's very intuitive.\NBut it's already been resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You didn't kill her, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Mama?! Don't you trust me?!\NI only shot her leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot her once and erased her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe what I'm hearing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pudding-san? I thought that \Nyou were a very nice girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. You're our precious bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she tries to get revenge,\Nit'd be a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your concern, Mama.\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...thanks to her, I got to try my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I definitely can riddle Germa's \Nmodified human bodies with bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great. You're such a smart girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:10:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow,\Nyour gunfire will be the cue for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A decorated hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unending applause and laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appearing there is the groom Sanji
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and our sweet bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wedding kiss\Nwill draw everyone's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, with his goofy face, will try to lift your veil\Nand kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he sees your third eye for the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment he sees his beautiful bride's\Ncreepy real face,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll fall back a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:11:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the moment! Okay?\NKill him with one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim at the spot between his eyebrows.\NIt's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pudding-san will kill Sanji-san?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone there will be stunned and frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of Germa will become upset\Nand as they turn around and run,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll already be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless guns will be pointing at\Nthe unarmed Vinsmokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be no time for them to be scared\Nbefore their blood spatters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like fireworks,\Nthe sound of gunshots won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rain of bullets that'll keep piercing through\Ntheir bodies even after they die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pool of blood expands on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lifeless forms of the six Vinsmokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gunshots will become shots of joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the real party begins there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's celebrate with a cake!\NLet's celebrate with tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they lose their useless leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the whole of Germa will become mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:26.29,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,SANJI'S ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the groom - Sanji-{\i1}sama{\i0} surely is\Nsleeping in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't let him out or let anyone in until morning.\NKeep close watch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I fell asleep-{\i1}nasu{\i0}!\NIn Sanji-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he not back yet-{\i1}nasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he won't come \Nback any time soon-{\i1}nasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then let's sleep \Na little bit more-{\i1}nasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:06.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,MEETING ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:10.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Pekoms was with them until Chocolat Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:13.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Their objective is to take Sanji back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:18.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,There were six of them when Pudding \Nlured them to this main island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul King is in Mama's hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro detonated himself in the Courtyard\Non the third floor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed-{\i1}cock-a-doo{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of the four who entered the Seducing \NWoods, a rabbit and a raccoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...got caught by Big Sis Brulee -\Nshe reported so at noon today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means four out of the six of them are out.\NThe problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...these two who took down Big Bro Cracker\Nand got out of the Seducing Woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:14:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We surely locked them up\Nin the underground Prison Library.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there a rumor that they broke out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one of us was\Nthere in the Prison Library.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Big Brother Opera?\NThey say Jimbei appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's groundless!\NDon't make me repeat myself-{\i1}fa{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no information-{\i1}fa{\i0}!\NNo one has come to the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I promised to Mama, I was torturing\NLola's whereabouts out of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't know anything\Nso I burned them to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I went a little too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't you trust your brother, Montd'Or?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:15:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't say that I failed \Nto guard them! Never!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mama will take all of my lifespan away-fa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are Sanji and the Vinsmokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are all in their rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's all good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the intruders have been caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, in the giant kitchen,\Nthey're preparing for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make it a great wedding tomorrow\Nfor our precious sister Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Expand the coverage and patrol until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:16:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't trust Opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off of the island with \Nthe Straw Hats, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I can't do that!\NEven if I could, what about Baratie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about that after you escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay here, we're all gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:17:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a good thing that\Nwe widened our search to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can't hit them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy... Did I make this for Pudding-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are all their favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forget them! Forget them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we finally beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...gotta get back... to that spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:20:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have to worry about Luffy and the others.\NThey can flee on their own.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All members of the evil army \NVinsmoke will die. I'll die too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as Big Mom planned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's for the best.\NThat way our enemies get what they want.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It feels short but it was a fulfilling life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Vinsmoke Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Montd'Or said you were sleeping in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't come back, I'll be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...starving to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That meat is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.85,0:22:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a loud noise from that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:23:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I doing?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tiptoe silently, stealthy.\NSave Brook, sleeping alongside the Emperor!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In an extremely tense situation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Straw Hats try to invade Big Mom's \Nincredibly destructive bedroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they can't wake her up no matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.04,0:23:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Emperor Rolls Over! Rescue Brook Mission!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
